aqshell_header packed

Detailed Description

Aqueduct shell implementation.

This header contains declarations that are used by the code that implements a special shell for running Aqueduct experiments. This file is included by both src/mos/net/aqueduct_shell.c, which is MOS code, and src/apps/deluge_test/aqshell.c, which is XMOS code. The constants defined in this header are duplicated in src/apps/deluge_test/ExperServer.java.
